  "special": {
    "title": "Fandir? Thirteen.",
    "description": "Adds extra critical-hit damage on top of the usual Jakobs shotgun bonus. It also has an unusually tiny spread and higher zoom, trading some base damage and much higher recoil for that precision."
  },
  "notes": "Zer0 gains less from it than you might expect compared with a same-level purple Scattergun, but the precision still helps land pellets on weak points. Salvador gets reliable ranged damage even from the hip, and Gaige can use it well with Anarchy because the accuracy offsets some of the penalties and the magazine can shrink to 1 for easy stacking. Axton benefits from recoil control, and a Jakobs grip can raise the magazine to 4 rounds. Its high crit profile also suits Nisha's Showdown in The Pre-Sequel.",
